{
  "timestamp": "2026-05-01T17:47:33.712Z",
  "level": "INFO",
  "type": "DB_QUERY",
  "collection": "blogs",
  "method": "insertOne",
  "query": {
    "title": "We Lost Reliability and Credibility Because Our Founder Fell in Love with AI",
    "slug": "fell-in-love-with-ai",
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "data": {
          "text": "Introduction",
          "level": 4
        },
        "_id": "69f4e735dc7e87b78f548759"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "Today was the day I finally felt it — that sick, heavy feeling when you realize all your hard work, discipline, and professionalism have been completely wasted."
        },
        "_id": "69f4e735dc7e87b78f54875a"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "Our flagship product, ConnectAI — a SaaS platform serving the healthcare industry — went down for over four hours because our founder decided he knows better than everyone else. And the worst part? He didn’t just make a mistake. He made it with full arrogance, fueled by his blind faith in AI."
        },
        "_id": "69f4e735dc7e87b78f54875b"
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "data": {
          "text": "What Actually Happened",
          "level": 5
        },
        "_id": "69f4e735dc7e87b78f54875c"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "At 2 p.m. today, without any warning, our founder bypassed the entire CI/CD pipeline and directly pushed changes to production."
        },
        "_id": "69f4e735dc7e87b78f54875d"
      },
      {
        "type": "list",
        "data": {
          "items": [
            "No code review.",
            "No testing.",
            "No staging environment.",
            "Nothing."
          ],
          "ordered": false
        },
        "_id": "69f4e735dc7e87b78f54875e"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "He single-handedly rewrote the deployment logic because, apparently, “AI can handle it better.” The result? The initial SSH step itself failed. Backend APIs started crashing. Users got completely locked out of the application. For more than four painful hours, our healthcare clients — who depend on us for critical operations — couldn’t access the system."
        },
        "_id": "69f4e735dc7e87b78f54875f"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "And we? We were left scrambling like headless chickens trying to fix something that shouldn’t have broken in the first place."
        },
        "_id": "69f4e735dc7e87b78f548760"
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "data": {
          "text": "The Root Cause",
          "level": 5
        },
        "_id": "69f4e735dc7e87b78f548761"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "After hours of debugging, my colleague and I discovered the ugly truth."
        },
        "_id": "69f4e735dc7e87b78f548762"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "Our founder didn’t just “tweak” the deployment process — he completely destroyed the stable, well-tested CI/CD pipeline we had built over months. Every safety net, every validation step, every automated check we carefully put in place was wiped out and replaced with his half-baked, AI-generated nonsense."
        },
        "_id": "69f4e735dc7e87b78f548763"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "He didn’t consult anyone. He didn’t value anyone’s input."
        },
        "_id": "69f4e735dc7e87b78f548764"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "Why would he? In his head, he’s the visionary founder who’s discovered that AI can replace developers. The rest of us are just expensive liabilities slowing him down."
        },
        "_id": "69f4e735dc7e87b78f548765"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "This isn’t just about one bad deployment. This is about an entitled superior complex — the belief that because he’s the founder, his judgment is flawless and our years of experience are worthless."
        },
        "_id": "69f4e735dc7e87b78f548766"
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "data": {
          "text": "How It Feels",
          "level": 5
        },
        "_id": "69f4e735dc7e87b78f548767"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "Honestly? I feel demotivated as hell."
        },
        "_id": "69f4e735dc7e87b78f548768"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "I joined this company because I believed in building something reliable for the healthcare sector. I poured my skills, late nights, and attention to detail into making our systems stable and professional."
        },
        "_id": "69f4e735dc7e87b78f548769"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "And today, all of that was casually thrown away in one reckless move by someone who thinks he’s smarter than the entire engineering team combined."
        },
        "_id": "69f4e735dc7e87b78f54876a"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "Watching him act like a joker while calling himself a tech visionary is exhausting. The disrespect towards the team’s effort is beyond frustrating. It makes you question why you’re even trying anymore."
        },
        "_id": "69f4e735dc7e87b78f54876b"
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "data": {
          "text": "Lessons I Wish We Didn’t Have to Learn This Way",
          "level": 5
        },
        "_id": "69f4e735dc7e87b78f54876c"
      },
      {
        "type": "list",
        "data": {
          "items": [
            "AI is a tool",
            "not a replacement for human judgment and experience.",
            "When a founder starts believing his own hype and thinks he can replace processes with “AI magic",
            "” the whole company suffers.",
            "Technical decisions should never be made from ego and delusion."
          ],
          "ordered": false
        },
        "_id": "69f4e735dc7e87b78f54876d"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "We had reliability. We had credibility. We lost both today — not because of bad engineers, but because of one man’s arrogance and unrealistic faith in AI solving everything."
        },
        "_id": "69f4e735dc7e87b78f54876e"
      },
      {
        "type": "quote",
        "data": {
          "text": "Final Thoughts I’m tired."
        },
        "_id": "69f4e735dc7e87b78f54876f"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "Tired of watching years of careful engineering work being casually dismantled by someone who thinks he’s above the rules. Tired of seeing hard-working developers treated like they’re disposable. Tired of this growing delusion in tech that AI can magically replace everything without consequences."
        },
        "_id": "69f4e735dc7e87b78f548770"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "If you’re a founder reading this — understand one thing: Your developers are not obstacles. They are the ones who actually keep your product alive when your AI experiments fail."
        },
        "_id": "69f4e735dc7e87b78f548771"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "Today, we didn’t just lose four hours of uptime."
        },
        "_id": "69f4e735dc7e87b78f548772"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "We lost trust.\nWe lost motivation.\nAnd worst of all — we lost respect for the person leading us."
        },
        "_id": "69f4e735dc7e87b78f548773"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "I don’t know how long I can keep working in an environment where effort is dismissed and reckless decisions are celebrated as “bold moves.”"
        },
        "_id": "69f4e735dc7e87b78f548774"
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "data": {
          "text": "Because right now, it just feels pointless."
        },
        "_id": "69f4e735dc7e87b78f548775"
      }
    ],
    "excerpt": "",
    "author": "69f4d0621048fe75c7bb4a22",
    "featuredImage": "",
